# shadcn/ui & Tailwind conventions

- **cn utility**: Use `cn` from `lib/utils.ts` for class merging.
- **Class names**: Prefer semantic utility classes; avoid long arbitrary values. Keep component styles colocated.
- **Component additions**: Use shadcn generator via `bunx shadcn@latest add <component>`.
- **Radix primitives**: Keep accessible structure; expose `className` passthrough on root as needed.
- **Design tokens**: Follow Tailwind v4 utilities and `next-themes` for dark mode; avoid inline styles.
- **File placement**: New primitives under `components/ui/`; higher-level composites under `components/`.
- **Do not** rename exported component symbols without refactoring all imports.

References:

- `lib/utils.ts` (mdc:lib/utils.ts)
- `components/ui/*` (mdc:components/ui)
